{"tid":1974360,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個你誤解左好耐既歷史/地理","createTime":"2020-04-15T19:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T18:09:30.000Z","uid":54930,"like":3,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"2046eaf11cece3712ef8044931239630e988ed6f","tid":1974360,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:26:00.000Z","msg":"一戰係歐洲之間第一次打仗<br />\n冷戰時期真係全世界冇打過任何仗<br />\n日本戰國時期發生於接近中國三國時期<br />\n美國黑人係美洲原住民<br />\n中國同印度之間冇任何國家(中亞國家)<br />\n菲律賓同印尼係中亞國家<br />\n印尼人同印度人係同一個種族<br />\n昆士蘭，新西蘭， 奧克蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撒哈拉同哈薩克<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海南島係國家<br />\n老撾，蘇丹，不丹，也門係中國入面<br />\n馬達加斯加同哥倫比亞係美國入面<br />\n巴布亞新幾內亞係非洲<br />\n芬蘭係北極，聖誕老人住係果度"},{"pid":"7d061cd164f2f6ae76f485b81a4f4b06fecbcb6d","tid":1974360,"uid":224701,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:29:27.000Z","msg":"小學一直認為Toronto 係加拿大首都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到中學先知原來Ottawa先係"},{"pid":"8eb0a128813002e736d55f54012ef4b85c549b86","tid":1974360,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"7d061cd164f2f6ae76f485b81a4f4b06fecbcb6d","tid":1974360,"uid":224701,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:29:27.000Z","msg":"小學一直認為Toronto 係加拿大首都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到中學先知原來Ottawa先係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:30:23.000Z","msg":"唔係架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有溫哥華"},{"pid":"471b8c30a138c3bb6c96012e8bb56d46821b0dc6","tid":1974360,"uid":282501,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"冷戰冇打過仗嘅意思係？<br />\n<br />\n韓戰 越戰 都已經有打仗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049890d9a5563c69fc9a97f98f7461cbe1d4fba2","tid":1974360,"uid":54930,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"471b8c30a138c3bb6c96